Description: Used but absolutely like new. No scratches dings or blemishes. Used in home only for a short time. Includes the really nice padded gig bag that came with it. This is exactly as it came from the factory - setup could be a little better. The St. Vincent Signature Series 6 String Electric Guitar from Sterling offers many of the features of the Ernie Ball Music Man model at a more affordable price point. Unique in design, it offers a perfect combination of style, balance, versatility and playability. Includes gig bag. Signature design A completely new, refreshing design, featuring a perfectly balanced, bevel-top African Mahogany body, Rock Maple neck and Rosewood fretboard with St. Vincent signature fretboard inlays. Versatile tones An amazing array of tonal variations are available from the three specially voiced, Music Man specification mini-humbuckers which are selected by a custom configured 5 way switch Tuning stability The two-point, bent steel saddle "Vintage Tremolo", oversized Music Man 4 + 2 headstock providing straight string pull, and factory equipped Ernie Ball Slinky strings keep you in tone and in tune.
